<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٧٥٥ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5775">‌ابْنُ الْمُقْرِئِ </a>،<span class="c5"> قَالَ:</span> ثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2478">‌سُفْيَانُ </a>، عَنِ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5917">‌الزُّهْرِيِّ </a>، عَنِ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/1446">‌الْحَسَنِ</a> <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3903">‌وَعَبْدِ اللهِ ابْنَيْ مُحَمَّدٍ </a>-<span class="c5"> قَالَ:</span> وَكَانَ الْحَسَنُ أَوْثَقَهُمَا - عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5823">‌أَبِيهِمَا </a>أَنَّ النَّبِيَّ صَلَّى اللهُ عَلَيْهِ وَسَلَّمَ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>⦗٢٥٨⦘<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span> <span class="c2">«نَهَى عَنْ نِكَاحِ الْمُتْعَةِ، وَعَنْ لُحُومِ الْحُمُرِ الْأَهْلِيَّةِ زَمَنَ خَيْبَرَ»</span>.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">وَكَانَ سُفْيَانُ يَقُولُ:</span> كَانَ الْحَسَنُ خَيْرَهُمَا.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>